oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Wedding reception, Frank and Charlotte Adkins
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Newlyweds Frank and Charlotte Nicodemus Adkins pose with Charlotte's sister, Suzanna Nicodemus, and her future husband, Arthur Gilkey. Frank and Charlotte were married November 11, 1942. On verso, "Wedding of Frank Edward Adkins and Charlotte Nicodemus on 11/11/42".
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Weddings
